''Shinobi'' is [[unlockable (gaming)|unlockable]] in ''[[Sonic's Ultimate Genesis Collection]]'' for the [[PlayStation 3]] and Xbox 360 after the first round of ''[[Shinobi III: Return of the Ninja Master]]'' without using a continue.

